蓬佩奥于1986年与莱斯利·利伯特·凯恩（Leslie Libert Cain，1964年3月23日-）结婚<ref name="TopHonor"/>，于1997年離婚，凯恩現居[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]][[银泉_(马里兰州)|银泉]]。2000年，他与苏珊·贾斯特·莫斯特鲁斯（Susan Justice Mostrous，1965年2月1日-）结婚，並收養了蘇珊第一次婚姻中生育的兒子尼古拉斯（Nicholas William Pompeo，1990年9月26日-）<ref>[https://www.factsninja.com/things-you-didnt-know-about-mike-pompeos-wife-susan-pompeo.html 《Things You Didn’t Know about Mike Pompeo’s Wife, Susan Pompeo》：“Susan Pompeo was born Susan Justice Mostrous, on February 1, 1965, in Wichita, Kansas, United States.”“Mike Pompeo had married Leslie Libert in 1986. The couple divorced in 1997.”“Susan and Mike got married in 2000. Following this, Mike adopted Susan’s son, Nicholas (or “Nick”), who was born out of Susan’s previous marriage.”]</ref>。蘇珊出生於[[堪萨斯州|堪萨斯州]][[威奇托_(堪萨斯州)|威奇托]]，畢業於[[卫奇塔州立大学|卫奇塔州立大学]]通訊專業，畢業後就職於私人銀行15年，曾任{{link-en|Emprise Bank}}高級副總裁。蘇珊在丈夫政治職業生涯中影響巨大，積極支持蓬佩奧的國會競選活動<ref>{{Cite web|title=Who is Susan Pompeo? Everything You Need to Know|url=https://www.thefamouspeople.com/profiles/susan-pompeo-42744.php|accessdate=2020-07-09|work=www.thefamouspeople.com|language=en-US}}</ref>。

蓬佩奥是一個[[基督徒|基督徒]]，隶属于{{link-en|福音派长老会 (美国)|Evangelical Presbyterian Church (United States)|福音派长老会}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kansas.com/living/religion/article1076672.html|title=Eastminster church decides to break from denomination|work=kansas|access-date=2018-03-13|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314042828/http://www.kansas.com/living/religion/article1076672.html|archive-date=2018-03-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kansas.com/living/religion/article209327599.html|title=Mike Pompeo's Wichita church calls for prayer over confirmation process|work=The Wichita Eagle|last=Burgess|first=Katherine|access-date=2018-04-22|date=2018-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180422070117/http://www.kansas.com/living/religion/article209327599.html|archive-date=2018-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年至2009年，担任当地教会的[[执事_(基督教)|执事]]，并擔任[[主日学|主日学]]的[[探題|探題]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://religionnews.com/2018/04/19/5-faith-facts-about-mike-pompeo-a-divisive-devotion/|title=5 faith facts about Mike Pompeo: A divisive devotion|last=Jenkins|first=Jack|date=2018-04-19|website=Religion News Service|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715163155/https://religionnews.com/2018/04/19/5-faith-facts-about-mike-pompeo-a-divisive-devotion/|archive-date=2019-07-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，蓬佩奥对一个教会团体说，基督徒需要“知道[[耶稣基督|耶稣基督]]是我们的[[救世主|救世主]]，是真正解决我们这个世界問題的唯一办法。”<ref>{{cite web|last1=Price|first1=Greg|title=Watch: Mike Pompeo faces 'no more war' protest during first confirmation hearing for Secretary of State|url=http://www.newsweek.com/pompeo-protest-war-hearing-state-883602|work=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]]|access-date=2018-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427084938/http://www.newsweek.com/pompeo-protest-war-hearing-state-883602|archive-date=2018-04-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，蓬佩奥在一个教会的演讲中说：“政治是一场永无止境的斗争......直到[[被提|被提]]。”<ref>{{cite web|first1=Michelle|last1=Goldberg|title=This Evil Is All Around Us|url=http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/politics/2017/01/mike_pompeo_trump_s_pick_for_the_cia_wants_a_holy_war.html|website=[[Slate_(magazine)|Slate]]|publisher=[[The_Slate_Group|The Slate Group]]|location=San Francisco, California|date=2017-01-12|access-date=2018-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427005626/http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/politics/2017/01/mike_pompeo_trump_s_pick_for_the_cia_wants_a_holy_war.html|archive-date=2018-04-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>

